The 'Fall' term in the '2023-2024' academic year refers to the Fall semester of the school year that begins in 2023 and ends in 2024; 
The enrollment status 'enrolled' or 'completed' indicates that a student has either registered for a course or finished it; 
The 'available' availability status means that the course has open seats for the given term and academic year.

